{"tid":1698699,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【歷史台】雅典大學明年將開辦首個英語授課的希臘史課程","createTime":"2019-11-07T16:22:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T07:42:10.000Z","uid":120678,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"79162375b54ea295444d0dc93783f78c00016d93","tid":1698699,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T16:22:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://greece.greekreporter.com/files/University-of-Athens-1-e1571842115283.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgreece.greekreporter.com%2Ffiles%2FUniversity-of-Athens-1-e1571842115283.jpg&h=eb2d47ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位愛好希臘古典史，又渴望到歐洲留學的網友們，我想在此向大家分享一個好消息。根據希臘媒體報導，希臘雅典大學(National and Kapodistrian University of Athens)將於2020年9月開辦希臘首個完全以英語授課的「古希臘考古、歷史和文學的文學士」(BA Program in Archaeology, History, and Literature of Ancient Greece)課程。課程由雅典大學哲學院主辦，跟香港的學士學位一樣是四年制，2020年1月起接受報名，該課程將面向國際收生，報讀者必須為非歐盟居民(non-EU citizens)，換言之港澳、台灣的高中生將可以報讀該課程。課程除了以英語講授外，學費將定為6,000歐元(約52,000港幣)，預計第一屆招收100名學生。完成課程後，將可累積248分獲歐盟承認的學分。<br />\n詳情請參閱以下報導或大學官方網頁：<br />\n<a href=\"https://greece.greekreporter.com/2019/10/23/university-of-athens-will-offer-first-english-language-bachelors-degree-in-greece/?fbclid=IwAR0yD7xAo5XQfxxCkxF003Xf2NKgDBlOgkrJDP25CAkxjfxI_PTWdqZUIbY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgreece.greekreporter.com%2F2019%2F10%2F23%2Funiversity-of-athens-will-offer-first-english-language-bachelors-degree-in-greece%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0yD7xAo5XQfxxCkxF003Xf2NKgDBlOgkrJDP25CAkxjfxI_PTWdqZUIbY&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK%2F4XLRjZdTHGp6sdrEQ6olc%3D&h=37618c58\" target=\"_blank\">https://greece.greekreporter.com/2019/10/23/university-of-athens-will-offer-first-english-language-bachelors-degree-in-greece/?fbclid=IwAR0yD7xAo5XQfxxCkxF003Xf2NKgDBlOgkrJDP25CAkxjfxI_PTWdqZUIbY</a>"},{"pid":"b76ab38d38086c0d6519950d564244f21f91f05f","tid":1698699,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T16:57:32.000Z","msg":"幾好奇會係咩人讀